page.title: 01LENGTH OF RESIDENCE
page.content:
In our survey we asked the people living within our area how long they had lived in our area. These are the results we obtained ;
1. 36, or 31% of the total surveyed had lived here for less than 5 years.
2. 22, or 19% of the total had lived here for between 6 & 10 years.
{3.}17, or 14% of the total had lived here for between 11 & 15 years.
{4.}19, or 16% of the total had lived here for between 16 & 20 years.
{5.}Four, or 3% of the total had lived here for between 21 & 25 years.
